<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>早上，灰姑娘听继姐姐们聊天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们还在谈论王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他爱上了那个公主。”特鲁迪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他要去找她！”格特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘擦掉了眼泪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“王子永远都找不到我。”她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后来，国王的信使来到了城里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他吹响了喇叭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>继母和继姐姐们跑了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘跟着她们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听着，各位！”信使说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“王子发现了一只水晶鞋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每一位淑女都必须试穿一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子会和适合水晶鞋的人结婚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格特笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许那鞋适合我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“或者我！”特鲁迪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>继母瞪着她们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它会适合你们其中一个的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>信使走遍了城里的每家每户。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个姑娘都试穿了那只水晶鞋，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但没有人适合。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，信使来到了灰姑娘的家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘正在打扫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先，格特坐了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃......呃......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用力想穿上那只鞋，但鞋子不适合她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你起来，格特。”继母说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在轮到特鲁迪了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特鲁迪想用力穿上那只鞋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鞋子不合适。”她伤心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰姑娘放下了扫帚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我呢？”她问道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以试试鞋吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>